[[File:Black armour set (lg) equipped.png|thumb|130px|A player with black armour equipped.]]
'''Black equipment''' are items made from [[Metal#Black|black metal]]. Black equipment is stronger than [[steel equipment]], yet weaker than [[mithril equipment]]. As the name suggests, the equipment is black in colour. Black armour requires 10 [[Defence]] to wield, melee weapons require 10 [[Attack]] to wield and ranged weapons 10 [[Ranged]]. Black equipment is almost identical to [[white equipment]], unlocked after the [[Wanted!]] quest, however, white equipment is member's only and has a slight [[Prayer]] bonus.

A set of black armour is used in the [[King's Ransom]] quest and in [[Heroes' Quest]] (helmet, platebody and platelegs). In Heroes' Quest, you will only need the black armour if you're part of the [[Black Arm Gang]]. For [[King's Ransom]], a [[black plateskirt]] will also suffice instead of the platelegs.

Black items '''''cannot''''' be [[smithing|smithed]].

==Weapons==
'''Black weapons''' require an [[Attack]] level of 10 to wield.

