==Armour==
'''Black armour''' is the fourth-lowest quality [[armour]] in the standard spectrum of metal armours ([[Bronze equipment#Armour|bronze]] to [[Dragon equipment#Armour|dragon]]). Black armour requires 10 [[Defence]] to wear.

{{Infotable Bonuses|Black med helm|Black full helm|Black chainbody|Black platebody|Black platelegs|Black plateskirt|Black sq shield|Black kiteshield|Black boots|Black gloves|Black defender#Normal|sort=dslash|nototals=yes}}

==Other==
Ornamental black armour, such as [[Black heraldic armour|heraldic]] and [[Black trimmed armour|trimmed]], have the same bonuses as standard black armour. These can be obtained from the member's only [[Treasure Trails]] minigame.

'''Note:''' Other players '''''cannot''''' trim or bless armour. Players claiming to do so are scammers.
